BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO EDUCATION -- THE EDUCATION EQUITY AND PROPERTY TAX
RELIEF ACT
***
1 This act would amend categorical state funding to include excess costs associated with
2 transporting homeless students to out-of-district public schools. This act would also provide that
3 certain nonprofit nonpublic schools would share in the cost of transporting students with the
4 sending school districts.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
